    {
      "id": "seg-007-title",
      "startTime": 22.92,
      "endTime": 26.2,
      "text": "When the old woman moved from the shoe.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": false,
      "contentType": "intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-007",
      "startTime": 26.2,
      "endTime": 30.96,
      "text": "There was once a little goblin woman who had six sons.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-009",
      "startTime": 30.96,
      "endTime": 38.120000000000005,
      "text": "They were very ugly, little boys with brown, whizzing faces, and eyes as black as",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-010",
      "startTime": 38.120000000000005,
      "endTime": 41.24,
      "text": "slow as they had very big heads.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-011",
      "startTime": 41.24,
      "endTime": 47.760000000000005,
      "text": "Though they were so fat, their legs were so thin, you wouldn't believe.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-012",
      "startTime": 47.760000000000005,
      "endTime": 53.72,
      "text": "Now the little goblin woman thought the world of her six little sons, and she had given",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-013",
      "startTime": 53.72,
      "endTime": 56.44,
      "text": "them all pretty far names.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-014",
      "startTime": 56.44,
      "endTime": 63.12,
      "text": "Slower, butch-up, soirl, bluebell, cow slip, and dandelion.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-015",
      "startTime": 63.12,
      "endTime": 69.52,
      "text": "The little goblin woman was very poor, but the way she managed was something wonderful.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-016",
      "startTime": 69.52,
      "endTime": 75.4,
      "text": "She and her little family lived in a hollow tree with a little garden rounded.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-017",
      "startTime": 75.4,
      "endTime": 81.32,
      "text": "There were three floors inside, and the little string ladder connected the rooms.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-018",
      "startTime": 81.32,
      "endTime": 86.32,
      "text": "The first floor was a kitchen, who was ever so clean and cozy.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-019",
      "startTime": 86.32,
      "endTime": 92.88,
      "text": "Then it was here that the family had meals and sat in the cold winter evenings, round",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-020",
      "startTime": 92.88,
      "endTime": 98,
      "text": "a little twig fire, listening to the wind and rain outside.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-021",
      "startTime": 98,
      "endTime": 103.52,
      "text": "The next floor was a bedroom, and the top floor was the drawing room.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-022",
      "startTime": 103.52,
      "endTime": 109.75999999999999,
      "text": "Its walls were decorated with colored leaves, and it was here that visitors were received.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-023",
      "startTime": 110.24000000000001,
      "endTime": 116.56,
      "text": "Well, one cold, rainy evening, the whole family was sitting round the kitchen fire, drinking",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-024",
      "startTime": 116.56,
      "endTime": 117.56,
      "text": "broth.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-025",
      "startTime": 117.56,
      "endTime": 120.08000000000001,
      "text": "When the little goblin woman said,",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-026",
      "startTime": 120.08000000000001,
      "endTime": 125.08000000000001,
      "text": "\"'Dandelion, it's your turn to fetch the water tonight, dearie.'\"",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-027",
      "startTime": 125.08000000000001,
      "endTime": 131.48000000000002,
      "text": "\"'Yes, Mom,' said Dandelion, and taking his last drink of broth, he ran to wash his acorn",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-028",
