      "startTime": 311.76,
      "endTime": 313.88,
      "text": "\"'Perhaps,' he said softly.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-071",
      "startTime": 313.88,
      "endTime": 318.8,
      "text": "\"'If he didn't whip them, they do as they were told.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-072",
      "startTime": 318.8,
      "endTime": 323.03999999999996,
      "text": "The old dame looked at him in astonishment.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-073",
      "startTime": 323.03999999999996,
      "endTime": 329.2,
      "text": "And perhaps the broth isn't so nice as what mum makes,\" added Dandelion.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-074",
      "startTime": 329.2,
      "endTime": 333,
      "text": "\"'They couldn't cry if they had a cup of her broth.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-075",
      "startTime": 333,
      "endTime": 335.96,
      "text": "\"'Dear me!\" cried the old woman.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-076",
      "startTime": 335.96,
      "endTime": 337.08,
      "text": "\"'What next?\"",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-077",
      "startTime": 337.08,
      "endTime": 340.52,
      "text": "\"'You come and see my mum,' said Dandelion.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-078",
      "startTime": 340.52,
      "endTime": 342.15999999999997,
      "text": "\"'Have a talk to her.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-079",
      "startTime": 342.15999999999997,
      "endTime": 345.52,
      "text": "I'll call for you when I fetch the water.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-080",
      "startTime": 345.52,
      "endTime": 348.56,
      "text": "\"'Well, now,' said the old dame.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-081",
      "startTime": 348.56,
      "endTime": 351.15999999999997,
      "text": "\"'It ain't often I go on a little visit.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-082",
      "startTime": 351.15999999999997,
      "endTime": 353.56,
      "text": "It'll be a change.\"",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-083",
      "startTime": 353.56,
      "endTime": 355.4,
      "text": "And she put on her bonnets.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-084",
      "startTime": 356.15999999999997,
      "endTime": 361.79999999999995,
      "text": "That night the old woman woke the children up, gave them each a kiss, which surprised",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-085",
      "startTime": 361.79999999999995,
      "endTime": 362.79999999999995,
      "text": "them very much.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-086",
      "startTime": 362.79999999999995,
      "endTime": 364.91999999999996,
      "text": "But they were still more astonished.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-087",
      "startTime": 364.91999999999996,
      "endTime": 368,
      "text": "And she gave them each some broth with bread.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-088",
      "startTime": 368,
      "endTime": 374,
      "text": "\"'My dears,' she said, \"'you're going to have bread in your broth every night.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-089",
      "startTime": 374,
      "endTime": 377.79999999999995,
      "text": "And I've got a new soup recipe in my pocket.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-090",
      "startTime": 377.79999999999995,
      "endTime": 381.2,
      "text": "What's more, you've all been asked out to tea tomorrow.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-091",
      "startTime": 381.2,
      "endTime": 384.79999999999995,
      "text": "So I'm going to put your hair and curl papers.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-092",
      "startTime": 385.8,
      "endTime": 387.6,
      "text": "\"'Oh no, no!\"",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-093",
      "startTime": 387.6,
      "endTime": 388.6,
      "text": "Scream the children.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-094",
      "startTime": 388.6,
      "endTime": 393.40000000000003,
      "text": "\"'You'll pull, then we shall cry, and you'll beat us.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-095",
      "startTime": 393.40000000000003,
      "endTime": 398.96000000000004,
      "text": "\"'I ain't going to beat you no more,' my dears,' said the old woman, kissing them",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-096",
      "startTime": 398.96000000000004,
      "endTime": 399.96000000000004,
      "text": "all again.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-097",
      "startTime": 399.96000000000004,
      "endTime": 402.48,
      "text": "\"'I've learned a lesson.\"",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-098",
      "startTime": 402.48,
      "endTime": 404.92,
      "text": "\"'Come in my dear.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-099",
      "startTime": 404.92,
      "endTime": 407.48,
      "text": "Come in!' cried Mrs. Goblin.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-100",
      "startTime": 407.48,
      "endTime": 413.44,
      "text": "\"'I've lit a fire in the dryroom so he can have a little talk while the children play",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-101",
      "startTime": 413.44,
      "endTime": 414.44,
      "text": "in the kitchen.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-102",
      "startTime": 414.44,
      "endTime": 418.84,
      "text": "\"'And now, my dear,' she added, when they were alone.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-103",
      "startTime": 418.84,
      "endTime": 420.96,
      "text": "\"'Now you're here.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-104",
      "startTime": 420.96,
      "endTime": 423.64,
      "text": "What's to hinder you from stopping?'",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-105",
      "startTime": 423.64,
      "endTime": 426.84,
      "text": "The old woman was crying for joy.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-106",
      "startTime": 426.84,
      "endTime": 430.84,
      "text": "\"'But so many children!' she said presently.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-107",
      "startTime": 430.84,
      "endTime": 438.8,
      "text": "\"'The more that may air, we'll all live together and be as happy as the night is short.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-108",
      "startTime": 438.8,
      "endTime": 441.68,
      "text": "And so they did.",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": true,
      "contentType": "main"
    },
    {
      "id": "seg-109",
      "startTime": 443.44,
      "endTime": 446.34,
      "text": "And of section 6.\"",
      "translationHint": "",
      "keywords": [],
      "phraseNotes": [],
      "wordTimings": [],
      "enabledForPractice": false,
      "contentType": "note"
    }
  ]
}
